    tags: 'nworld, AJ and Sharlien Liao, about us',
    content: "<div class=\"section-title-1-min\"><h4><span>A few words about us</span></h4><hr></div><div class=\"box-content animated-2 fadeIn-animation in-view\"><p><strong>NWORLD PRODUCTS ONLINE BY AJSHARLIEN LIAO</strong> is an online store of an authorized dealer/distributor of Alphanetword,NWorld Philippines. This website is to serve you nworld products just a click away! Please feel free to contact us with your questions and concerns about our international transactions.</p><p>This website does not represent Alphanetworld Corporation  as an entity but represents as Registered Ntrepreneur of Alphanetworld Corporation who is solely responsible for the overall management and operation of this website.</p></div><div class=\"section-title-1-min\"><h4><span>NWORLD ALPHANETWORLD CORPORATION</span></h4><hr></div><div class=\"box-content animated-2 fadeIn-animation in-view\"><p>Alphanetworld Corporation, or NWORLD, is a corporation committed to its motivated, self-driven, and passionate independent distributors or the so called Ntrepreneurs and to the society and government as well. The company was founded by Mr. Juluis Allan G. Nolasco, a network marketer by passion, a top executive by profession and a seasoned businessman.</p><p>NWORLD is engaged in the marketing of premium health and beauty products, using distinctive method of product distribution through direct selling.</p><p>Duly incorporated and registered on July 9, 2015 with the Securities and Exchange Commission under Company Registration Number CS201513594, NWORLD has a paid up capital of One Hundred Million Pesos (PHP100,000,000.00).</p></div><div class=\"section-title-1-min\"><h4><span>PRODUCT DISTRIBUTION</span></h4><hr></div><div class=\"box-content animated-2 fadeIn-animation in-view\"><p>We own and formulate our products. Exclusively distributed by NWorld through direct selling or direct marketing with point system marketing program. A financial rewards of our  innovative, dynamic, sustainable, and profitable business opportunity while honing distributors to become a seasoned entrepreneurs.</p></div><div class=\"section-title-1-min\"><h4><span>MANUFACTURING</span></h4><hr></div><div class=\"box-content animated-2 fadeIn-animation in-view\"><p>Products are made abroad, a GMP (Good Manufacturing Practices) - Publicly Listed Manufacturing Company in Korea. Others are made locally made raw materials are abroad.</p></div><div class=\"section-title-1-min\"><h4><span>Want to be an Ntrepreneur?</span></h4><hr></div><div class=\"box-content animated-2 fadeIn-animation in-view\"><p>Feel free to email us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:ajlien@nworldproductsonline.com\">ajlien@nworldproductsonline.com</a></p>"
  },

